11#ifndef MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTP_SENDER_VIDEO_FRAME_TRANSFORMER_DELEGATE_H_
12#define MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTP_SENDER_VIDEO_FRAME_TRANSFORMER_DELEGATE_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/frame_transformer_interface.h"
17#include "api/scoped_refptr.h"
18#include "api/task_queue/task_queue_base.h"
19#include "api/video/video_layers_allocation.h"
20#include "rtc_base/synchronization/mutex.h"
21
22namespace webrtc {
23
24class RTPSenderVideo;
25
26// Delegates calls to FrameTransformerInterface to transform frames, and to
27// RTPSenderVideo to send the transformed frames. Ensures thread-safe access to
28// the sender.
29class RTPSenderVideoFrameTransformerDelegate : public TransformedFrameCallback {
30 public:
31 RTPSenderVideoFrameTransformerDelegate(
32 RTPSenderVideo* sender,
33 rtc::scoped_refptr<FrameTransformerInterface> frame_transformer,
34 uint32_t ssrc,
35 TaskQueueBase* send_transport_queue);
36
37 void Init();
38
39 // Delegates the call to FrameTransformerInterface::TransformFrame.
40 bool TransformFrame(int payload_type,
41 absl::optional<VideoCodecType> codec_type,
42 uint32_t rtp_timestamp,
43 const EncodedImage& encoded_image,
44 RTPVideoHeader video_header,
45 absl::optional<int64_t> expected_retransmission_time_ms);
46
47 // Implements TransformedFrameCallback. Can be called on any thread. Posts
48 // the transformed frame to be sent on the |encoder_queue_|.
49 void OnTransformedFrame(
50 std::unique_ptr<TransformableFrameInterface> frame) override;
51
52 // Delegates the call to RTPSendVideo::SendVideo on the |encoder_queue_|.
53 void SendVideo(std::unique_ptr<TransformableFrameInterface> frame) const;
54
55 // Delegates the call to RTPSendVideo::SetVideoStructureAfterTransformation
56 // under |sender_lock_|.
57 void SetVideoStructureUnderLock(
58 const FrameDependencyStructure* video_structure);
59
60 // Delegates the call to
61 // RTPSendVideo::SetVideoLayersAllocationAfterTransformation under
62 // |sender_lock_|.
63 void SetVideoLayersAllocationUnderLock(VideoLayersAllocation allocation);
64
65 // Unregisters and releases the |frame_transformer_| reference, and resets
66 // |sender_| under lock. Called from RTPSenderVideo destructor to prevent the
67 // |sender_| to dangle.
68 void Reset();
69
70 protected:
71 ~RTPSenderVideoFrameTransformerDelegate() override = default;
72
73 private:
74 mutable Mutex sender_lock_;
75 RTPSenderVideo* sender_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(sender_lock_);
76 rtc::scoped_refptr<FrameTransformerInterface> frame_transformer_;
77 const uint32_t ssrc_;
78 TaskQueueBase* encoder_queue_ = nullptr;
79 TaskQueueBase* send_transport_queue_;
80};
81
82} // namespace webrtc
83
84#endif // MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTP_SENDER_VIDEO_FRAME_TRANSFORMER_DELEGATE_H_
